00:27:51.840 --> 00:27:54.342 align:middle line:90%
Let's try it again.
I think you're better than that.

00:27:54.342 --> 00:27:56.261 align:middle line:90%
- Where's the virus?
- I didn't ask to dance.

00:27:56.261 --> 00:27:58.054 align:middle line:90%
And why should I talk to you?
You're not CIA.

00:27:58.054 --> 00:27:59.305 align:middle line:84%
No? How do you know that?

00:27:59.305 --> 00:28:01.099 align:middle line:84%
Where shall I start?

00:28:01.099 --> 00:28:02.600 align:middle line:84%
There's two types of CIA agents.

00:28:02.600 --> 00:28:03.810 align:middle line:84%
Intelligence and espionage.

00:28:03.810 --> 00:28:05.645 align:middle line:90%
Those guys over there
can barely lift a pencil.

00:28:05.645 --> 00:28:07.230 align:middle line:84%
That's what intelligence agents look like.

00:28:07.230 --> 00:28:09.899 align:middle line:90%
You look like you could
pick up a building.

00:28:09.899 --> 00:28:11.401 align:middle line:84%
But espionage is about blending in

00:28:11.401 --> 00:28:12.485 align:middle line:84%
and about being subtle,

00:28:12.485 --> 00:28:16.948 align:middle line:84%
and there is nothing subtle about you.

00:28:16.948 --> 00:28:18.366 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

00:28:18.366 --> 00:28:20.326 align:middle line:84%
That's good.

00:28:20.326 --> 00:28:22.161 align:middle line:90%
- I'm impressed.
- I didn't kill anybody.

00:28:22.161 --> 00:28:25.123 align:middle line:84%
I know you didn't.

00:28:25.123 --> 00:28:26.332 align:middle line:84%
How do you know that, then?

00:28:26.332 --> 00:28:27.500 align:middle line:84%
Because you can learn a lot

00:28:27.500 --> 00:28:28.835 align:middle line:84%
about somebody when you fight them.

00:28:28.835 --> 00:28:30.753 align:middle line:84%
And when we fought,

00:28:30.753 --> 00:28:32.338 align:middle line:84%
you weren't fighting to kill me.

00:28:32.338 --> 00:28:35.091 align:middle line:84%
You were fighting to run away.

00:28:35.091 --> 00:28:36.509 align:middle line:84%
But either way, the world thinks that

00:28:36.509 --> 00:28:37.886 align:middle line:84%
you're a murderer and a thief,

00:28:37.886 --> 00:28:39.012 align:middle line:84%
so you're not going anywhere

00:28:39.012 --> 00:28:40.263 align:middle line:84%
or getting any goddamn phone call

00:28:40.263 --> 00:28:41.598 align:middle line:84%
until you give me some real answers.

00:28:41.598 --> 00:28:43.183 align:middle line:84%
You have no idea what is happening here.

00:28:43.183 --> 00:28:44.267 align:middle line:84%
Then tell me. Help me understand.

00:28:44.267 --> 00:28:45.351 align:middle line:84%
