00:28:45.351 --> 00:28:46.728 align:middle line:90%
Then I can't either...
You're wasting time!

00:28:46.728 --> 00:29:01.326 align:middle line:90%
Virus gets in the wrong hands,
that's it. It's game over.

00:29:01.326 --> 00:29:03.036 align:middle line:84%
Does that mean it's time for curls?

00:29:03.036 --> 00:29:05.914 align:middle line:90%
Just like the CIA,
always flexing the wrong muscle.

00:29:05.914 --> 00:29:07.457 align:middle line:90%
You know, the mind is the
strongest muscle in the body.

00:29:07.457 --> 00:29:08.583 align:middle line:84%
Maybe you should try exercising that

00:29:08.583 --> 00:29:10.835 align:middle line:84%
a little bit more.

00:29:10.835 --> 00:29:12.462 align:middle line:84%
"There's more wisdom in your body

00:29:12.462 --> 00:29:14.339 align:middle line:84%
"than in your deepest philosophies."

00:29:14.339 --> 00:29:16.925 align:middle line:84%
Ooh, let me guess. That Bruce Lee?

00:29:16.925 --> 00:29:19.594 align:middle line:84%
No, Nietzsche.

00:29:19.594 --> 00:29:21.888 align:middle line:84%
'Cause I'm flexing this.

00:29:21.888 --> 00:29:25.934 align:middle line:84%
And all of that.

00:29:25.934 --> 00:29:28.061 align:middle line:84%
Come here.

00:29:28.061 --> 00:29:29.938 align:middle line:84%
If she moves, I want you to shoot her.

00:29:29.938 --> 00:29:31.439 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, he can't shoot me.

00:29:31.439 --> 00:29:33.233 align:middle line:90%
- Yeah, not allowed.
- In the face.

00:29:33.233 --> 00:29:34.734 align:middle line:90%
You can't. Not in the face.
You'd go to prison.

00:29:34.734 --> 00:29:35.902 align:middle line:84%
You can shoot her right in the face.

00:29:35.902 --> 00:29:37.278 align:middle line:84%
No, you can't. You'd go to prison. Sorry.

00:29:37.278 --> 00:29:41.366 align:middle line:90%
I want you to shoot her
two times right in that face.

00:29:41.366 --> 00:29:49.707 align:middle line:90%
- Okay?
- Yeah.

00:29:49.707 --> 00:29:50.792 align:middle line:84%
Hi, Dad.

00:29:50.792 --> 00:29:52.293 align:middle line:84%
Did you catch the hot spy lady?

00:29:52.293 --> 00:29:54.921 align:middle line:90%
Come on. It's me.
I catch everybody I hunt.

00:29:54.921 --> 00:29:57.382 align:middle line:84%
How long have you been doing this?

00:29:57.382 --> 00:30:05.557 align:middle line:84%
'Cause you seem... new.

00:30:05.557 --> 00:30:07.016 align:middle line:84%
She's actually quite annoying.

00:30:07.016 --> 00:30:08.476 align:middle line:84%
You know, Dad,

00:30:08.476 --> 00:30:10.311 align:middle line:84%
