00:30:12.730 --> 00:30:17.318 align:middle line:84%
Where'd you hear that from?

00:30:17.318 --> 00:30:18.403 align:middle line:84%
Okay, look,

00:30:18.403 --> 00:30:20.405 align:middle line:90%
uh, me and the spy lady,
we're not flirting, all right?

00:30:20.405 --> 00:30:36.171 align:middle line:84%
Zero chemistry.

00:30:36.171 --> 00:30:37.547 align:middle line:84%
I don't know.

00:30:37.547 --> 00:30:38.715 align:middle line:84%
When you saw her photo,

00:30:38.715 --> 00:30:40.466 align:middle line:84%
you definitely gave the eyebrow.

00:30:40.466 --> 00:30:41.801 align:middle line:84%
What eyebrow?

00:30:41.801 --> 00:30:43.553 align:middle line:84%
You know, Dad, that thing that you do.

00:30:43.553 --> 00:30:45.930 align:middle line:84%
What thing?

00:30:45.930 --> 00:30:47.223 align:middle line:90%
- I don't do that.
- Yes, you do.

00:30:47.223 --> 00:30:49.184 align:middle line:84%
No, I don't... I definitely don't do that.

00:30:49.184 --> 00:30:50.268 align:middle line:84%
I don't even know what you're doing.

00:30:50.268 --> 00:30:52.353 align:middle line:84%
That's the silliest thing I've ever seen.

00:30:52.353 --> 00:30:54.355 align:middle line:90%
Let me get going,
I got business to take care of.

00:30:54.355 --> 00:30:56.816 align:middle line:90%
I'll see you when I get home, okay?
I love you.

00:30:56.816 --> 00:30:57.901 align:middle line:84%
Love you.

00:30:57.901 --> 00:31:04.115 align:middle line:84%
Hey, one more thing.

00:31:04.115 --> 00:31:13.541 align:middle line:84%
Goddamn it.

00:31:13.541 --> 00:31:15.126 align:middle line:90%
This is not the dance
you wanna do with me, woman.

00:31:15.126 --> 00:31:17.378 align:middle line:90%
- Oh, really?
- I eat bullets all day long.

00:31:17.378 --> 00:31:20.215 align:middle line:90%
Oh, for breakfast and lunch?
'Cause it's dinnertime.

00:31:20.215 --> 00:31:22.008 align:middle line:84%
I'll count down for you. Three...

00:31:22.008 --> 00:31:23.760 align:middle line:90%
- Two...
- Hobbs.

00:31:23.760 --> 00:31:25.803 align:middle line:90%
- Freeze.
- Put that down.

00:31:25.803 --> 00:31:27.764 align:middle line:90%
Get your greasy
sausage fingers off of her.

00:31:27.764 --> 00:31:30.391 align:middle line:90%
- What are you doing here?
- Saving you.

00:31:30.391 --> 00:31:31.726 align:middle line:84%
I don't need to be saved.

00:31:31.726 --> 00:31:33.520 align:middle line:84%
No, no, no. This is my house

00:31:33.520 --> 00:31:35.146 align:middle line:90%
and your goddamn girlfriend
ain't going anywhere.

00:31:35.146 --> 00:31:36.981 align:middle line:90%
- That's disgusting.
- "Girlfriend"?

00:31:36.981 --> 00:31:41.361 align:middle line:84%
That is my sister.

00:31:41.361 --> 00:31:42.445 align:middle line:84%
Bullshit.

00:31:42.445 --> 00:31:43.571 align:middle line:84%
She's too good-looking to be your sister.

00:31:43.571 --> 00:31:44.822 align:middle line:84%
Very funny. Hat.

00:31:44.822 --> 00:31:47.033 align:middle line:90%
- There are people after you.
- Believe me, I know that.

00:31:47.033 --> 00:31:48.117 align:middle line:84%
It's gonna stay that way

00:31:48.117 --> 00:31:49.369 align:middle line:84%
unless you tell me where that virus is.

00:31:49.369 --> 00:31:50.620 align:middle line:84%
Listen to me, pinhead.

00:31:50.620 --> 00:31:52.747 align:middle line:90%
She's gonna die if I don't
get her out of here right now!

00:31:52.747 --> 00:31:53.831 align:middle line:84%
We're all gonna die

00:31:53.831 --> 00:31:55.041 align:middle line:90%
if she doesn't tell us
where that weapon is.

00:31:55.041 --> 00:31:58.336 align:middle line:90%
Actually, everyone's gonna die
'cause I am the virus!

00:31:58.336 --> 00:31:59.754 align:middle line:84%
It's embedded in capsules.

00:31:59.754 --> 00:32:28.700 align:middle line:84%
I need to find a way to get them out.

00:32:28.700 --> 00:32:59.397 align:middle line:84%
Bag the asset.

00:32:59.397 --> 00:33:00.481 align:middle line:84%
Now or never.

00:33:00.481 --> 00:33:01.858 align:middle line:84%
I'm more of a now type of guy.

00:33:01.858 --> 00:33:04.319 align:middle line:90%
- On my three.
- Sure.

00:33:04.319 --> 00:33:08.281 align:middle line:84%
One, two, three.

00:33:08.281 --> 00:34:32.156 align:middle line:84%
No one tells me what to do.

00:34:32.156 --> 00:34:51.092 align:middle line:84%
Now I take you to school, son.

00:34:51.092 --> 00:34:53.845 align:middle line:90%
Deckard Shaw.
It's been a long time.

00:34:53.845 --> 00:34:55.138 align:middle line:84%
Good to see you, Brixton.

00:34:55.138 --> 00:34:57.015 align:middle line:84%
I think you're out of bullets there, son.

00:34:57.015 --> 00:34:58.099 align:middle line:84%
Lucky for you, I am.

00:34:58.099 --> 00:35:00.894 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

00:35:00.894 --> 00:35:02.562 align:middle line:90%
- Nice suit.
- Bulletproof.

00:35:02.562 --> 00:35:04.314 align:middle line:90%
- State of the art.
- Could've done with that

00:35:04.314 --> 00:35:05.648 align:middle line:84%
the last time I put a bullet in ya.

00:35:05.648 --> 00:35:07.192 align:middle line:84%
No, actually, it was three bullets.

00:35:07.192 --> 00:35:08.610 align:middle line:84%
Two to the chest, one to the head.

00:35:08.610 --> 00:35:10.862 align:middle line:84%
Just like they taught us. Do you remember?

00:35:10.862 --> 00:35:12.822 align:middle line:84%
It's a shame you didn't join Eteon.

00:35:12.822 --> 00:35:14.240 align:middle line:84%
You could've had all this, my friend.

00:35:14.240 --> 00:35:15.450 align:middle line:90%
- "Friend"?
- Yeah.

00:35:15.450 --> 00:35:19.913 align:middle line:90%
- You're not the man I knew.
- No. I am way better.

00:35:19.913 --> 00:35:48.441 align:middle line:84%
I'm the future of mankind.

00:35:48.441 --> 00:35:50.068 align:middle line:84%
Stop!

00:35:50.068 --> 00:35:53.112 align:middle line:84%
Stop!

00:35:53.112 --> 00:35:55.281 align:middle line:84%
Hattie, get in the car.

00:35:55.281 --> 00:35:57.200 align:middle line:84%
We're all going.

00:35:57.200 --> 00:35:58.701 align:middle line:84%
Not you.

00:35:58.701 --> 00:36:00.453 align:middle line:84%
Just the girl.

00:36:00.453 --> 00:36:11.548 align:middle line:84%
I said, we're all going.

00:36:11.548 --> 00:36:35.905 align:middle line:84%
Disable the car. I need the girl alive.

00:36:35.905 --> 00:36:37.574 align:middle line:84%
What the hell did you do, Hattie?

00:36:37.574 --> 00:36:39.075 align:middle line:84%
A big brother lecture now, really? Huh?

00:36:39.075 --> 00:36:40.201 align:middle line:84%
I injected myself. I didn't have a choice.

00:36:40.201 --> 00:36:53.923 align:middle line:84%
He was gonna take it.

00:36:53.923 --> 00:37:20.700 align:middle line:84%
Program intercepting vector.

00:37:20.700 --> 00:38:19.092 align:middle line:84%
You might wanna...

00:38:19.092 --> 00:38:22.929 align:middle line:84%
Might be time for some curls.

00:38:22.929 --> 00:38:28.351 align:middle line:84%
Let go of me.

00:38:28.351 --> 00:38:32.564 align:middle line:84%
Very good.

00:38:32.564 --> 00:38:33.648 align:middle line:84%
You wanna tell me

00:38:33.648 --> 00:38:35.525 align:middle line:90%
just what in the fresh turkey hell
we're dealing with here?

00:38:35.525 --> 00:38:37.026 align:middle line:84%
Long story.

00:38:37.026 --> 00:38:39.279 align:middle line:84%
He's a ghost. Supposed to be dead.

00:38:39.279 --> 00:38:41.531 align:middle line:90%
Eight years ago,
I put a bullet through his brain.

00:38:41.531 --> 00:38:48.830 align:middle line:90%
Great, so we're being chased
by the Terminator.

00:38:48.830 --> 00:38:49.914 align:middle line:84%
I don't think he's gonna make it.

00:38:49.914 --> 00:38:51.583 align:middle line:90%
Well, I don't think he can see
over the steering wheel.

00:38:51.583 --> 00:39:51.100 align:middle line:90%
Buckle up, fat boy,
I'm gonna save your life again.

00:39:51.100 --> 00:39:54.687 align:middle line:84%
You want a war, then?

00:39:54.687 --> 00:40:09.827 align:middle line:84%
Okay.

00:40:09.827 --> 00:40:19.921 align:middle line:84%
Okay, ride's over. We gotta lose this car.

00:40:19.921 --> 00:40:21.464 align:middle line:84%
Update.

00:40:21.464 --> 00:40:23.007 align:middle line:84%
I've hacked the mainframe

00:40:23.007 --> 00:40:24.884 align:middle line:84%
of every news agency and outlet.

00:40:24.884 --> 00:40:26.094 align:middle line:84%
How many do we control?

00:40:26.094 --> 00:40:28.471 align:middle line:90%
Hundred and seventy-four
broadcasts, 2,000 odd.

00:40:28.471 --> 00:40:31.015 align:middle line:90%
Double it.
I want 100% control of this story.

00:40:31.015 --> 00:40:33.059 align:middle line:90%
- Standard frame job.
- No, standard will not do.

00:40:33.059 --> 00:40:34.644 align:middle line:84%
I need something special for these guys.

00:40:34.644 --> 00:40:36.437 align:middle line:84%
So listen up. Narrative:

00:40:36.437 --> 00:40:41.234 align:middle line:90%
Hobbs, Shaw, big guy,
little guy, have been ID'd.

00:40:41.234 --> 00:40:44.737 align:middle line:90%
They've been blamed for
the recent attacks on the CIA.

00:40:44.737 --> 00:40:47.699 align:middle line:90%
They shared a prison cell
where they hatched a plan

00:40:47.699 --> 00:40:51.411 align:middle line:84%
to start their reign of terror.

00:40:51.411 --> 00:40:55.331 align:middle line:84%
Just got real.

00:40:55.331 --> 00:40:57.083 align:middle line:84%
Who the hell are these guys?

00:40:57.083 --> 00:40:59.586 align:middle line:84%
Eteon. They're a secret tech cult,

00:40:59.586 --> 00:41:02.797 align:middle line:90%
with a mercenary army
and plenty of dark money.

00:41:02.797 --> 00:41:04.424 align:middle line:84%
And delusions of saving the world

00:41:04.424 --> 00:41:06.259 align:middle line:84%
by augmenting the human race.

00:41:06.259 --> 00:41:07.677 align:middle line:84%
That's it.

00:41:07.677 --> 00:41:09.387 align:middle line:84%
Apparently they control the media as well.

00:41:09.387 --> 00:41:11.806 align:middle line:84%
Heard rumors about these people.

00:41:11.806 --> 00:41:14.100 align:middle line:84%
Everybody thinks they're a myth.

00:41:14.100 --> 00:41:16.477 align:middle line:90%
I've seen it firsthand
how real they are.

00:41:16.477 --> 00:41:18.021 align:middle line:84%
If you don't fit into their plans,

00:41:18.021 --> 00:41:19.522 align:middle line:84%
you've already dug your own grave.

00:41:19.522 --> 00:41:21.149 align:middle line:90%
All right, let's get to the
nearest lockdown facility...

00:41:21.149 --> 00:41:23.109 align:middle line:84%
Hey, no, no, no. You don't get it, do you?

00:41:23.109 --> 00:41:24.819 align:middle line:84%
Brixton's a tier-one assassin.

00:41:24.819 --> 00:41:26.696 align:middle line:84%
Best I've ever seen. I know him.

00:41:26.696 --> 00:41:28.990 align:middle line:90%
He ain't never gonna stop
until he gets that virus.

00:41:28.990 --> 00:41:32.785 align:middle line:90%
And besides, that's my sister.
Family business.

00:41:32.785 --> 00:41:34.120 align:middle line:84%
Is your name Shaw? No.

00:41:34.120 --> 00:41:35.330 align:middle line:84%
Then she's going nowhere with you.

00:41:35.330 --> 00:41:36.706 align:middle line:84%
When it comes to the fate of the world,

00:41:36.706 --> 00:41:37.790 align:middle line:84%
it becomes my business.

00:41:37.790 --> 00:41:39.042 align:middle line:84%
I don't care if she's your sister,

00:41:39.042 --> 00:41:40.251 align:middle line:84%
that woman ain't going anywhere...

00:41:40.251 --> 00:41:41.377 align:middle line:90%
- Where are you going?
- I'm going away.

00:41:41.377 --> 00:41:43.129 align:middle line:90%
I don't have time for your
alpha male shit right now.

00:41:43.129 --> 00:41:44.214 align:middle line:84%
You're both idiots.

00:41:44.214 --> 00:41:45.381 align:middle line:84%
