Oh, no. No backsies. What's the matter?

01:05:00.401 --> 01:05:01.986 align:middle line:90%
You got a lot of bad guys
behind that door?

01:05:01.986 --> 01:05:40.024 align:middle line:84%
Watch this. You might learn something.

01:05:40.024 --> 01:06:38.416 align:middle line:84%
Watch this.

01:06:38.416 --> 01:06:41.044 align:middle line:84%
Enter corresponding match.

01:06:41.044 --> 01:06:43.421 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:06:43.421 --> 01:06:47.759 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:06:47.759 --> 01:06:56.976 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:06:56.976 --> 01:07:01.981 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:01.981 --> 01:07:05.527 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:05.527 --> 01:07:06.694 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:06.694 --> 01:07:08.071 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:08.071 --> 01:07:10.532 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:10.532 --> 01:07:14.786 align:middle line:84%
Access denied.

01:07:14.786 --> 01:07:17.622 align:middle line:84%
You come and do it!

01:07:17.622 --> 01:07:21.417 align:middle line:84%
Access granted.

01:07:21.417 --> 01:07:30.760 align:middle line:84%
Doors opening.

01:07:30.760 --> 01:07:34.222 align:middle line:84%
Very good. Well done, boys.

01:07:34.222 --> 01:07:54.367 align:middle line:84%
I'm impressed that you even got in here.

01:07:54.367 --> 01:07:57.704 align:middle line:90%
Is this your first day
on the Death Star?

01:07:57.704 --> 01:08:01.082 align:middle line:84%
The syringe is ready.

01:08:01.082 --> 01:08:04.502 align:middle line:84%
Because you seem... new.

01:08:04.502 --> 01:08:19.475 align:middle line:84%
This will shut her up.

01:08:19.475 --> 01:08:28.026 align:middle line:90%
That... That's...
That's not possible.

01:08:28.026 --> 01:08:29.402 align:middle line:84%
No. What are you doing?

01:08:29.402 --> 01:08:34.490 align:middle line:84%
Having to extract it myself.

01:08:34.490 --> 01:08:59.098 align:middle line:84%
Wait!

01:08:59.098 --> 01:09:02.810 align:middle line:84%
There he is. Nice and rested?

01:09:02.810 --> 01:09:04.062 align:middle line:84%
Get your full eight hours?

01:09:04.062 --> 01:09:06.856 align:middle line:84%
I was gonna order some room service.

01:09:06.856 --> 01:09:07.941 align:middle line:84%
What do you fancy?

01:09:07.941 --> 01:09:09.651 align:middle line:84%
French toast? I'll get the order in.

01:09:09.651 --> 01:09:12.862 align:middle line:90%
I just dreamt they killed you
before I woke up.

01:09:12.862 --> 01:09:14.489 align:middle line:84%
Pretty disappointed right now.

01:09:14.489 --> 01:09:17.450 align:middle line:84%
It's a little elaborate, I must admit.

01:09:17.450 --> 01:09:19.619 align:middle line:84%
Old-school interrogation technique

01:09:19.619 --> 01:09:20.870 align:middle line:84%
we picked up in black ops.

01:09:20.870 --> 01:09:22.497 align:middle line:84%
Shock will kill a man in three.

01:09:22.497 --> 01:09:24.123 align:middle line:84%
Do you remember that, Deck?

01:09:24.123 --> 01:09:26.709 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, I remember
a lot of things from back then.

01:09:26.709 --> 01:09:28.962 align:middle line:90%
I reckon you've only got
four shocks in you, boys.

01:09:28.962 --> 01:09:30.713 align:middle line:84%
Yeah? I think we could take five.

01:09:30.713 --> 01:09:44.519 align:middle line:84%
"Five"? Well, all right.

01:09:44.519 --> 01:09:47.188 align:middle line:84%
You had to open your big mouth, didn't ya?

01:09:47.188 --> 01:10:07.333 align:middle line:90%
I thought it was a cool thing
to say in the moment.

01:10:07.333 --> 01:10:09.335 align:middle line:90%
Do you remember
when we were real brothers?

01:10:09.335 --> 01:10:12.046 align:middle line:90%
Task Force Black.
Do you remember that, Deck?

01:10:12.046 --> 01:10:14.424 align:middle line:90%
Man, we ended up
seeing the worst in people.

01:10:14.424 --> 01:10:16.467 align:middle line:84%
Worst in our countries, our leaders,

01:10:16.467 --> 01:10:19.137 align:middle line:84%
our enemies, our friends.

01:10:19.137 --> 01:10:20.972 align:middle line:90%
You don't know the meaning
of that word anymore.

01:10:20.972 --> 01:10:23.057 align:middle line:84%
But don't worry about it, neither does he.

01:10:23.057 --> 01:10:24.225 align:middle line:84%
He shoots them right in the head,

01:10:24.225 --> 01:10:26.436 align:middle line:90%
but in your case, I thought
it was hell of a good idea.

01:10:26.436 --> 01:10:27.604 align:middle line:84%
Big man, you still talking?

01:10:27.604 --> 01:10:35.904 align:middle line:90%
I said I thought it was
a hell of a good...

01:10:35.904 --> 01:10:37.947 align:middle line:84%
Oh!

01:10:37.947 --> 01:10:40.491 align:middle line:84%
Shit.

01:10:40.491 --> 01:10:42.952 align:middle line:90%
You know, it's funny how
humanity's hate for each other

01:10:42.952 --> 01:10:44.996 align:middle line:90%
is stronger than
its own self-preservation,

01:10:44.996 --> 01:10:46.331 align:middle line:84%
which is why we're here.

01:10:46.331 --> 01:10:47.707 align:middle line:84%
Remember eight years ago, Deck,

01:10:47.707 --> 01:10:49.959 align:middle line:84%
when Eteon asked us to join their mission?

01:10:49.959 --> 01:10:52.378 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you mean their death cult.

01:10:52.378 --> 01:10:54.589 align:middle line:90%
- They're lunatics.
- Visionaries.

01:10:54.589 --> 01:10:56.257 align:middle line:84%
Visionaries of a future.

01:10:56.257 --> 01:10:58.343 align:middle line:84%
A bigger future. A brighter future.

01:10:58.343 --> 01:11:00.345 align:middle line:84%
You remember the data they gave us, man.

01:11:00.345 --> 01:11:02.680 align:middle line:84%
What with environmental damage,

01:11:02.680 --> 01:11:04.766 align:middle line:84%
capitalism, terrorism,

01:11:04.766 --> 01:11:07.519 align:middle line:84%
humanity wipes itself out by 2096.

01:11:07.519 --> 01:11:09.062 align:middle line:84%
Now, that is scary to me.

01:11:09.062 --> 01:11:11.606 align:middle line:84%
But if we fulfill Eteon's vision,

01:11:11.606 --> 01:11:12.941 align:middle line:84%
you save their world.

01:11:12.941 --> 01:11:14.400 align:middle line:84%
You don't save the world with genocide.

01:11:14.400 --> 01:11:16.903 align:middle line:84%
Genocide, schmenocide.

01:11:16.903 --> 01:11:19.113 align:middle line:84%
You know what this virus is?

01:11:19.113 --> 01:11:35.839 align:middle line:90%
This virus is a necessary
shock to the system.

01:11:35.839 --> 01:11:39.092 align:middle line:84%
Whoo! That's three.

01:11:39.092 --> 01:11:40.176 align:middle line:84%
I love this thing.

01:11:40.176 --> 01:11:42.762 align:middle line:84%
Told you then, I'm telling you now,

01:11:42.762 --> 01:11:45.306 align:middle line:84%
your metrics are off.

01:11:45.306 --> 01:11:48.518 align:middle line:90%
One good reason:
You assume the worst in people.

01:11:48.518 --> 01:11:50.895 align:middle line:90%
People cannot be trusted
to do the right thing.

01:11:50.895 --> 01:11:52.021 align:middle line:84%
Look at the two of you.

01:11:52.021 --> 01:11:53.523 align:middle line:84%
The fate of the world is in your hands,

01:11:53.523 --> 01:11:55.400 align:middle line:84%
and you can't even get along.

01:11:55.400 --> 01:11:57.360 align:middle line:90%
But you know all about
doing the right thing,

01:11:57.360 --> 01:12:02.866 align:middle line:84%
don't you, Shaw? Yeah.

01:12:02.866 --> 01:12:06.995 align:middle line:84%
Little souvenir, huh, bro?

01:12:06.995 --> 01:12:10.957 align:middle line:90%
You come to kill me,
I'll do the same every time.

01:12:10.957 --> 01:12:15.670 align:middle line:84%
What'd you expect? A shiatsu?

01:12:15.670 --> 01:12:18.256 align:middle line:84%
Anyone talking to you?

01:12:18.256 --> 01:12:24.637 align:middle line:84%
Your mama.

01:12:24.637 --> 01:12:28.433 align:middle line:84%
Yeah!

01:12:28.433 --> 01:12:30.602 align:middle line:84%
I get it. You're still mad.

01:12:30.602 --> 01:12:34.606 align:middle line:90%
You're upset because,
hey, when you wouldn't turn,

01:12:34.606 --> 01:12:35.732 align:middle line:84%
they asked me to come and kill you

01:12:35.732 --> 01:12:36.816 align:middle line:84%
and, of course, I had to

01:12:36.816 --> 01:12:39.194 align:middle line:84%
because you knew too much.

01:12:39.194 --> 01:12:42.280 align:middle line:90%
But I think about that night a lot.
I think about it.

01:12:42.280 --> 01:12:45.200 align:middle line:90%
Because what I realize now
that I did not realize then

01:12:45.200 --> 01:12:48.411 align:middle line:90%
is that when you shot me,
you gave me a gift.

01:12:48.411 --> 01:12:51.998 align:middle line:84%
Look at me. I'm black Superman.

01:12:51.998 --> 01:12:54.125 align:middle line:84%
Bulletproof, new spine,

01:12:54.125 --> 01:12:58.046 align:middle line:90%
and the more machine I become,
the more humane I am.

01:12:58.046 --> 01:13:00.548 align:middle line:84%
This is what you wanna fight for.

01:13:00.548 --> 01:13:03.468 align:middle line:90%
I'm giving you another chance
to join us, Deckard.

01:13:03.468 --> 01:13:05.762 align:middle line:84%
And the boss wants big mouth as well.

01:13:05.762 --> 01:13:07.805 align:middle line:84%
If not, I kill you both.

01:13:07.805 --> 01:13:11.851 align:middle line:84%
Which, honestly, I'd love to do.

01:13:11.851 --> 01:13:14.687 align:middle line:90%
You know Eteon.
You know what they're capable of.

01:13:14.687 --> 01:13:17.815 align:middle line:84%
They rebuilt me. Dismantled him.

01:13:17.815 --> 01:13:19.776 align:middle line:84%
Made it look like he killed his own team.

01:13:19.776 --> 01:13:26.491 align:middle line:84%
Even your own sister... disowned you.

01:13:26.491 --> 01:13:27.742 align:middle line:84%
Just say the word, bro.

01:13:27.742 --> 01:13:30.495 align:middle line:84%
Say the word and all of this goes away.

01:13:30.495 --> 01:13:32.956 align:middle line:84%
Your sister lives. His daughter lives.

01:13:32.956 --> 01:13:34.582 align:middle line:84%
We get you some upgrades,

01:13:34.582 --> 01:13:38.628 align:middle line:84%
and we go on to saving the world.

01:13:38.628 --> 01:13:39.754 align:middle line:84%
What's it to be?

01:13:39.754 --> 01:13:41.464 align:middle line:84%
Join the evolution of man,

01:13:41.464 --> 01:13:45.093 align:middle line:84%
or die with the weak?

01:13:45.093 --> 01:13:47.804 align:middle line:84%
Just get it done.

01:13:47.804 --> 01:13:50.932 align:middle line:90%
I told the boss
you wouldn't change your mind.

01:13:50.932 --> 01:13:52.016 align:middle line:84%
See you later.

01:13:52.016 --> 01:13:56.855 align:middle line:84%
Wait, wait, wait, wait. Wait!

01:13:56.855 --> 01:13:58.273 align:middle line:84%
I think we should join.

01:13:58.273 --> 01:14:01.943 align:middle line:84%
Join?

01:14:01.943 --> 01:14:04.112 align:middle line:84%
You said some really compelling things.

01:14:04.112 --> 01:14:05.780 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that black Superman thing,

01:14:05.780 --> 01:14:07.156 align:middle line:84%
that really got me. I love that.

01:14:07.156 --> 01:14:09.701 align:middle line:90%
What are you, deaf, stupid, or both?
We ain't joining.

01:14:09.701 --> 01:14:11.286 align:middle line:90%
There you go again,
you're just thinking about yourself.

01:14:11.286 --> 01:14:12.537 align:middle line:84%
You're such a diva.

01:14:12.537 --> 01:14:14.289 align:middle line:84%
What about my feelings, for once?

01:14:14.289 --> 01:14:15.373 align:middle line:84%
Let me tell you something,

01:14:15.373 --> 01:14:17.584 align:middle line:84%
if we were a band, you know who you'd be?

01:14:17.584 --> 01:14:18.918 align:middle line:84%
You'd be Mick Jagger.

01:14:18.918 --> 01:14:21.796 align:middle line:84%
"Mick Jagger"?

01:14:21.796 --> 01:14:23.339 align:middle line:84%
Mick Jagger.

01:14:23.339 --> 01:14:25.758 align:middle line:84%
Oi, what's it to be?

01:14:25.758 --> 01:14:32.223 align:middle line:84%
In or out?

01:14:32.223 --> 01:14:33.766 align:middle line:90%
- We're not gonna join.
- We're not gonna join.

01:14:33.766 --> 01:14:35.059 align:middle line:84%
But since you're standing there,

01:14:35.059 --> 01:14:36.436 align:middle line:84%
here's what I'm gonna do.

01:14:36.436 --> 01:14:38.188 align:middle line:84%
I'm gonna rip the arm off this chair.

01:14:38.188 --> 01:14:40.064 align:middle line:84%
I'm gonna smash him right in the face.

01:14:40.064 --> 01:14:42.025 align:middle line:90%
Stab him right in the neck
for looking that way.

01:14:42.025 --> 01:14:44.235 align:middle line:84%
Kill all 13 guys in seven seconds.

01:14:44.235 --> 01:14:45.570 align:middle line:84%
And here's what I'm gonna do.

01:14:45.570 --> 01:14:47.989 align:middle line:90%
I'm gonna slip out of these
chains and dropkick him,

01:14:47.989 --> 01:14:50.950 align:middle line:84%
him and him right in the throat.

01:14:50.950 --> 01:14:54.037 align:middle line:90%
No, not him, that's my guy.
You gotta pick another guy.

01:14:54.037 --> 01:14:55.830 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean that's your guy?
That's my guy.

01:14:55.830 --> 01:14:57.415 align:middle line:84%
No, no, no. That's face-smash guy.

01:14:57.415 --> 01:14:58.958 align:middle line:84%
You gotta find another dropkick guy.

01:14:58.958 --> 01:15:01.044 align:middle line:90%
You want a face-smash guy?
I'm gonna find you one.

01:15:01.044 --> 01:15:02.754 align:middle line:84%
See that guy over there?

01:15:02.754 --> 01:15:05.131 align:middle line:84%
The big one. The big one.

01:15:05.131 --> 01:15:07.133 align:middle line:90%
- That's face-smash guy.
- No, he's way too big.

01:15:07.133 --> 01:15:10.053 align:middle line:84%
Ain't that right, Hattie?

01:15:10.053 --> 01:15:11.179 align:middle line:84%
Let 'em go.

01:15:11.179 --> 01:15:15.600 align:middle line:90%
All right, boys, stay calm.
We need her alive.

01:15:15.600 --> 01:15:17.435 align:middle line:84%
Let them go, or what?

01:15:17.435 --> 01:15:19.562 align:middle line:90%
Or you're gonna get
a nice new breeze there

01:15:19.562 --> 01:15:20.813 align:middle line:84%
at the center of your forehead.

01:15:20.813 --> 01:15:23.316 align:middle line:84%
You're not gonna shoot me.

01:15:23.316 --> 01:15:26.319 align:middle line:90%
Because you need
an activation chip to fire that gun.

01:15:26.319 --> 01:15:27.695 align:middle line:84%
Sorry.

01:15:27.695 --> 01:15:33.743 align:middle line:84%
Try this gun!

01:15:33.743 --> 01:16:06.943 align:middle line:84%
I'm not small change.

01:16:06.943 --> 01:16:08.444 align:middle line:90%
- Let's roll.
- You think?

01:16:08.444 --> 01:16:46.024 align:middle line:84%
Dick.

01:16:46.024 --> 01:16:54.032 align:middle line:84%
There she is.

01:16:54.032 --> 01:16:56.659 align:middle line:90%
- Hattie, where's the machine?
- It's in the second truck.

01:16:56.659 --> 01:17:03.082 align:middle line:84%
On it.

01:17:03.082 --> 01:17:04.209 align:middle line:84%
Mick Jagger.

01:17:04.209 --> 01:17:12.842 align:middle line:84%
Never fails.

01:17:12.842 --> 01:17:21.309 align:middle line:84%
We're not out of this yet, Hattie.

01:17:21.309 --> 01:17:28.650 align:middle line:84%
Got the machine.

01:17:28.650 --> 01:17:51.840 align:middle line:90%
Get a move on!
Train's leaving the station!

01:17:51.840 --> 01:18:11.192 align:middle line:84%
That sumbitch really is black Superman.

01:18:11.192 --> 01:18:26.708 align:middle line:84%
Engage drones.

01:18:26.708 --> 01:18:29.460 align:middle line:84%
We're running out of road.

01:18:29.460 --> 01:18:38.595 align:middle line:84%
Hold on!

01:18:38.595 --> 01:19:06.414 align:middle line:84%
Route to intercept.

01:19:06.414 --> 01:19:16.382 align:middle line:84%
Ahh! Whoo!

01:19:16.382 --> 01:19:22.305 align:middle line:84%
On your left.

01:19:22.305 --> 01:19:48.122 align:middle line:84%
Brace yourself.

01:19:48.122 --> 01:19:51.292 align:middle line:84%
Hobbs, this ain't gonna make it.

01:19:51.292 --> 01:19:52.460 align:middle line:84%
Bringing her to ya.

01:19:52.460 --> 01:19:54.337 align:middle line:84%
You thinking what I'm thinking, Shaw?

01:19:54.337 --> 01:19:56.381 align:middle line:84%
Let's trade some paint.

01:19:56.381 --> 01:20:26.452 align:middle line:84%
Trade some paint.

01:20:26.452 --> 01:20:27.537 align:middle line:84%
Hattie.

01:20:27.537 --> 01:21:23.301 align:middle line:90%
- Huh?
- You trust me?

01:21:23.301 --> 01:21:24.928 align:middle line:84%
Gonna need a ride.

01:21:24.928 --> 01:21:26.387 align:middle line:84%
I know what you're thinking.

01:21:26.387 --> 01:21:39.651 align:middle line:84%
Just keep driving. I'll make it.

01:21:39.651 --> 01:21:55.500 align:middle line:84%
Take the wheel.

01:21:55.500 --> 01:21:58.211 align:middle line:84%
There he is.

01:21:58.211 --> 01:21:59.504 align:middle line:90%
- I got him.
- No, I got him.

01:21:59.504 --> 01:22:22.735 align:middle line:90%
- No, I got him.
- I got him.

01:22:22.735 --> 01:23:24.464 align:middle line:84%
I thought you were strong.

01:23:24.464 --> 01:23:26.007 align:middle line:84%
I'm sorry, brother.

01:23:26.007 --> 01:23:28.051 align:middle line:84%
This thing is really damaged.

01:23:28.051 --> 01:23:30.386 align:middle line:84%
Well, there goes option two.

01:23:30.386 --> 01:23:31.679 align:middle line:84%
That only leaves the first one.

01:23:31.679 --> 01:23:32.847 align:middle line:84%
Come on. Stop it, Hat.

01:23:32.847 --> 01:23:34.933 align:middle line:84%
I'm tired, Deck. I am done running.

01:23:34.933 --> 01:23:36.893 align:middle line:90%
- We still got time.
- "Time"?

01:23:36.893 --> 01:23:38.770 align:middle line:84%
Time for what? The machine's destroyed.

01:23:38.770 --> 01:23:40.438 align:middle line:90%
- Yeah, well, we'll fix it.
- How?

01:23:40.438 --> 01:23:42.023 align:middle line:90%
We need to find a place
to get off the grid.

01:23:42.023 --> 01:23:43.983 align:middle line:90%
Where?
We're wanted all over the world,

01:23:43.983 --> 01:23:45.068 align:middle line:84%
and Brixton won't stop.

01:23:45.068 --> 01:23:46.152 align:middle line:84%
We can't risk millions of people.

01:23:46.152 --> 01:23:47.445 align:middle line:84%
I told you on the plane,

01:23:47.445 --> 01:23:48.613 align:middle line:84%
we should've gone with option one.

01:23:48.613 --> 01:23:49.697 align:middle line:84%
It is done now, Deck.

01:23:49.697 --> 01:23:51.241 align:middle line:90%
- It's not done.
- It's done.

01:23:51.241 --> 01:23:55.078 align:middle line:84%
It's not done!

01:23:55.078 --> 01:23:59.207 align:middle line:84%
It's not done.

01:23:59.207 --> 01:24:00.583 align:middle line:84%
Look at me.

01:24:00.583 --> 01:24:01.918 align:middle line:84%
Remember that thing you used to say to me

01:24:01.918 --> 01:24:04.003 align:middle line:84%
when we were kids? Huh?

01:24:04.003 --> 01:24:05.296 align:middle line:84%
Used to look at me and say,

01:24:05.296 --> 01:24:08.007 align:middle line:84%
"Deck, it's never over till it's over."

01:24:08.007 --> 01:24:11.386 align:middle line:84%
We used to laugh. Remember that?

01:24:11.386 --> 01:24:17.308 align:middle line:90%
No, Deck, it went, "It's never
over till I say it's over."

01:24:17.308 --> 01:24:21.396 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, that was it.

01:24:21.396 --> 01:24:24.774 align:middle line:84%
So say it now. Say it.

01:24:24.774 --> 01:24:26.901 align:middle line:84%
Remember who we are.

01:24:26.901 --> 01:24:29.779 align:middle line:84%
We're the Shaw family.

01:24:29.779 --> 01:24:37.245 align:middle line:84%
We never, never, never give up.

01:24:37.245 --> 01:24:40.331 align:middle line:84%
We've got a day.

01:24:40.331 --> 01:24:42.333 align:middle line:84%
More than a day.

01:24:42.333 --> 01:24:46.504 align:middle line:84%
We don't even know where we'd go.

01:24:46.504 --> 01:24:50.216 align:middle line:84%
I know a place.

01:24:50.216 --> 01:24:51.676 align:middle line:84%
Where?

01:24:51.676 --> 01:24:57.348 align:middle line:90%
It's the last place on earth
I ever wanna go.

01:24:57.348 --> 01:25:18.369 align:middle line:84%
Home.

01:25:18.369 --> 01:25:20.079 align:middle line:84%
Abracadabra, bitches.

01:25:20.079 --> 01:25:22.081 align:middle line:84%
I told you that I could get you anything.

01:25:22.081 --> 01:25:24.501 align:middle line:84%
And listen to me, from Moscow to Samoa,

01:25:24.501 --> 01:25:26.169 align:middle line:84%
that is not an easy flight to charter,

01:25:26.169 --> 01:25:27.253 align:middle line:84%
but I got it done.

01:25:27.253 --> 01:25:28.755 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's why
we're calling you, Dinkley.

01:25:28.755 --> 01:25:29.839 align:middle line:84%
We just want to say thank you

01:25:29.839 --> 01:25:31.633 align:middle line:84%
for getting us that bird to Samoa.

01:25:31.633 --> 01:25:33.009 align:middle line:84%
Warriors help out warriors.

01:25:33.009 --> 01:25:34.385 align:middle line:84%
So all you need to know

01:25:34.385 --> 01:25:36.346 align:middle line:84%
is that you got a third squaddie over here

01:25:36.346 --> 01:25:39.098 align:middle line:90%
that is ready to go
whenever you need me to.

01:25:39.098 --> 01:25:42.560 align:middle line:84%
I'm just sitting in my lair.

01:25:42.560 --> 01:25:43.645 align:middle line:84%
You in a bathroom?

01:25:43.645 --> 01:25:45.021 align:middle line:84%
Potato, potah-to.

01:25:45.021 --> 01:25:46.940 align:middle line:84%
Wherever I am is where the magic happens.

01:25:46.940 --> 01:25:48.399 align:middle line:84%
We ain't gotta get into specifics.

01:25:48.399 --> 01:25:50.151 align:middle line:90%
Just to make sure
you got all the contacts.

01:25:50.151 --> 01:25:53.071 align:middle line:84%
You got the cell, you got my e-mail.

01:25:53.071 --> 01:25:54.447 align:middle line:90%
- Got 'em all.
- Imma shoot you

01:25:54.447 --> 01:25:55.615 align:middle line:84%
my mom number too.

01:25:55.615 --> 01:25:56.741 align:middle line:84%
Imma make sure you got that,

01:25:56.741 --> 01:25:58.660 align:middle line:84%
'cause if you can't get me, she can.

01:25:58.660 --> 01:26:00.328 align:middle line:90%
- Yeah.
- I got a Hotmail address

01:26:00.328 --> 01:26:01.704 align:middle line:84%
that's still active. Hit me on that.

01:26:01.704 --> 01:26:04.082 align:middle line:84%
LinkedIn. That's my profile.

01:26:04.082 --> 01:26:05.542 align:middle line:84%
...account thing I've been doing.

01:26:05.542 --> 01:26:06.835 align:middle line:84%
I'm just making sure you got everything...

01:26:06.835 --> 01:26:10.713 align:middle line:84%
We're losing ya.

01:26:10.713 --> 01:26:13.591 align:middle line:84%
That was my phone.

01:26:13.591 --> 01:26:14.884 align:middle line:84%
I hope this brother of yours

01:26:14.884 --> 01:26:17.512 align:middle line:84%
is as good a mechanic as you say he is.

01:26:17.512 --> 01:26:19.264 align:middle line:84%
Jonah is the best mechanic I know.

01:26:19.264 --> 01:26:20.974 align:middle line:84%
And he's gonna help us.

01:26:20.974 --> 01:26:41.077 align:middle line:84%
That is, if he doesn't kill me first.

01:26:41.077 --> 01:26:42.161 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, take your time.

01:26:42.161 --> 01:26:44.372 align:middle line:90%
It's only my sister's life
and the fate of the world

01:26:44.372 --> 01:26:48.668 align:middle line:84%
we're waiting on!

01:26:48.668 --> 01:26:49.752 align:middle line:84%
Oh, here we go.

01:26:49.752 --> 01:26:52.755 align:middle line:90%
Bet you a bullseye 50 quid
he punches him in the face.

01:26:52.755 --> 01:27:06.186 align:middle line:84%
Deal.

01:27:06.186 --> 01:27:09.355 align:middle line:84%
Jonah.

01:27:09.355 --> 01:27:12.066 align:middle line:84%
You know what comes next?

01:27:12.066 --> 01:27:16.404 align:middle line:84%
Yup.

01:27:16.404 --> 01:27:20.617 align:middle line:84%
See? Not just me.

01:27:20.617 --> 01:27:23.453 align:middle line:90%
Your face, it's all over
the bloody news, boy.

01:27:23.453 --> 01:27:25.079 align:middle line:84%
You're not welcome here, police.

01:27:25.079 --> 01:27:26.581 align:middle line:84%
You got a bloody cheek.

01:27:26.581 --> 01:27:29.209 align:middle line:84%
Coming here after 25 years.

01:27:29.209 --> 01:27:31.127 align:middle line:84%
Bringing your problems here to this house.

01:27:31.127 --> 01:27:34.130 align:middle line:90%
You betrayed our family,
bring shame on our house.

01:27:34.130 --> 01:27:37.300 align:middle line:84%
You betrayed your own blood!

01:27:37.300 --> 01:27:39.344 align:middle line:84%
Jonah, I hear you.

01:27:39.344 --> 01:27:40.428 align:middle line:84%
But we ain't kids anymore.

01:27:40.428 --> 01:27:41.513 align:middle line:84%
You better watch how you talk to me.

01:27:41.513 --> 01:27:44.098 align:middle line:90%
It's not the size of the dog
in the fight, boy.

01:27:44.098 --> 01:27:45.975 align:middle line:84%
It's the size of the fight in the dog.

01:27:45.975 --> 01:27:49.521 align:middle line:84%
No, it's always the size of the dog.

01:27:49.521 --> 01:27:53.775 align:middle line:90%
Hey! No fighting
under this roof, huh?

01:27:53.775 --> 01:27:58.071 align:middle line:84%
Is that my Luke?

01:27:58.071 --> 01:28:01.241 align:middle line:84%
My baby's home.

01:28:01.241 --> 01:28:03.243 align:middle line:84%
Hey, Mama.

01:28:03.243 --> 01:28:06.371 align:middle line:84%
Oka, I miss my baby boy.

01:28:06.371 --> 01:28:09.165 align:middle line:84%
But look at you, all skin and bones.

01:28:09.165 --> 01:28:12.001 align:middle line:90%
- Come over here and eat.
- No, no, no, Mama.

01:28:12.001 --> 01:28:13.837 align:middle line:84%
There's no time.

01:28:13.837 --> 01:28:15.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry.
I didn't want to bring trouble here.

01:28:15.380 --> 01:28:16.631 align:middle line:84%
You should've stayed away.

01:28:16.631 --> 01:28:18.341 align:middle line:84%
What did you bring here? What's going on?

01:28:18.341 --> 01:28:19.717 align:middle line:90%
- I brought the truth.
- What truth?

01:28:19.717 --> 01:28:20.927 align:middle line:84%
The truth is we were set up.

01:28:20.927 --> 01:28:23.179 align:middle line:90%
We were framed by people
who created a deadly virus.

01:28:23.179 --> 01:28:24.264 align:middle line:84%
Oh, come on.

01:28:24.264 --> 01:28:26.015 align:middle line:84%
It could go global if it's not stopped.

01:28:26.015 --> 01:28:27.809 align:middle line:84%
We could all die. All of us.

01:28:27.809 --> 01:28:29.936 align:middle line:90%
Everybody here in this fale,
everybody on the island.

01:28:29.936 --> 01:28:31.396 align:middle line:84%
And everybody around the world.

01:28:31.396 --> 01:28:33.565 align:middle line:90%
Jonah, I need you
to help fix this machine.

01:28:33.565 --> 01:28:35.191 align:middle line:84%
I need you to help my friends,

01:28:35.191 --> 01:28:37.485 align:middle line:90%
and I need us to build
defenses around here, now!

01:28:37.485 --> 01:28:38.987 align:middle line:84%
You think you can just come back in here

01:28:38.987 --> 01:28:40.071 align:middle line:84%
and we're gonna help you

01:28:40.071 --> 01:28:41.531 align:middle line:90%
- after everything you did?
- Yes!

01:28:41.531 --> 01:28:42.782 align:middle line:90%
- Not gonna happen!
- It's bigger than you and I!

01:28:42.782 --> 01:28:43.867 align:middle line:84%
I don't care!

01:28:43.867 --> 01:28:45.368 align:middle line:84%
It's bigger than you and I! We could die.

01:28:45.368 --> 01:28:48.955 align:middle line:90%
Good, because I would rather
die than help you, polo head!

01:28:48.955 --> 01:28:52.792 align:middle line:90%
Listen, I know your brother's
hard to be around, believe me.

01:28:52.792 --> 01:28:54.752 align:middle line:84%
But I trust him, and he brought us here

01:28:54.752 --> 01:28:56.254 align:middle line:84%
because this place has something

01:28:56.254 --> 01:28:59.174 align:middle line:84%
that nowhere else on the planet does: you.

01:28:59.174 --> 01:29:01.718 align:middle line:84%
You don't know me! I don't know you, okay?

01:29:01.718 --> 01:29:02.802 align:middle line:84%
Time for you all to go.

01:29:02.802 --> 01:29:04.762 align:middle line:90%
- Take your machine with you.
- Go, now!

01:29:04.762 --> 01:29:07.849 align:middle line:90%
- Go!
- Jonah Hobbs!

01:29:07.849 --> 01:29:10.185 align:middle line:84%
You have some respect for your uso.

01:29:10.185 --> 01:29:12.812 align:middle line:90%
If he needs anything,
we gonna give it to him.

01:29:12.812 --> 01:29:16.232 align:middle line:90%
The food off our tables,
the clothes off our backs,

01:29:16.232 --> 01:29:19.194 align:middle line:84%
even the mana of the island.

01:29:19.194 --> 01:29:23.072 align:middle line:84%
And you boys, all you boys,

01:29:23.072 --> 01:29:25.700 align:middle line:84%
you show our guests here fa'aaloalo,

01:29:25.700 --> 01:29:30.163 align:middle line:90%
or so help me God,
I'm gonna take this here slipper

01:29:30.163 --> 01:29:32.874 align:middle line:84%
and I'm gonna sasa your big, fat heads!

01:29:32.874 --> 01:29:35.418 align:middle line:84%
You boys hear me?

01:29:35.418 --> 01:29:37.378 align:middle line:84%
I'm sorry to bring this here, Mama.

01:29:37.378 --> 01:29:40.256 align:middle line:84%
Luke, this is your home.

01:29:40.256 --> 01:29:57.815 align:middle line:84%
We Samoans. We can handle troubles.

01:29:57.815 --> 01:30:00.276 align:middle line:84%
You were right.

01:30:00.276 --> 01:30:03.905 align:middle line:84%
You don't turn soldiers like them.

01:30:03.905 --> 01:30:07.158 align:middle line:84%
Do what I built you to do.

01:30:07.158 --> 01:30:10.870 align:middle line:84%
You're a one-of-a-kind war machine.

01:30:10.870 --> 01:30:13.498 align:middle line:84%
Bring us back my virus.

01:30:13.498 --> 01:30:16.835 align:middle line:84%
No handcuffs this time.

01:30:16.835 --> 01:30:20.129 align:middle line:84%
You can have your revenge.

01:30:20.129 --> 01:30:22.131 align:middle line:84%
I will.

01:30:22.131 --> 01:30:24.676 align:middle line:90%
We found 'em.
They hopped an emergency cargo plane.

01:30:24.676 --> 01:30:26.553 align:middle line:90%
- To where?
- Samoa.

01:30:26.553 --> 01:30:30.515 align:middle line:90%
Gentlemen! This is where
you earn your upgrades.

01:30:30.515 --> 01:30:48.074 align:middle line:84%
Bring me back my virus.

01:30:48.074 --> 01:30:58.710 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

01:30:58.710 --> 01:31:00.545 align:middle line:84%
It's quite the operation.

01:31:00.545 --> 01:31:03.089 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, for a chop shop.

01:31:03.089 --> 01:31:04.549 align:middle line:84%
Your dad was a car thief, then?

01:31:04.549 --> 01:31:07.802 align:middle line:90%
Ah, no.
My dad actually stole everything.

01:31:07.802 --> 01:31:09.888 align:middle line:84%
Drugs. Guns...

01:31:09.888 --> 01:31:11.806 align:middle line:84%
Sounds just like my family.

01:31:11.806 --> 01:31:13.892 align:middle line:90%
Mama raised us
till we were teenagers,

01:31:13.892 --> 01:31:16.311 align:middle line:90%
and my old man
started coming around again.

01:31:16.311 --> 01:31:18.813 align:middle line:84%
Taking a real interest in his sons.

01:31:18.813 --> 01:31:21.983 align:middle line:90%
The truth is,
he was just looking for a new crew.

01:31:21.983 --> 01:31:27.989 align:middle line:90%
And I was the only one
to see through those lies.

01:31:27.989 --> 01:31:31.409 align:middle line:90%
So the jobs my dad pulled
me and my brothers into

01:31:31.409 --> 01:31:35.496 align:middle line:84%
just got bigger and more dangerous.

01:31:35.496 --> 01:31:36.664 align:middle line:84%
Then eventually he knew,

01:31:36.664 --> 01:31:39.167 align:middle line:84%
and he was okay with,

01:31:39.167 --> 01:31:42.629 align:middle line:84%
getting me and my brothers killed.

01:31:42.629 --> 01:31:43.963 align:middle line:84%
So I turned him in.

01:31:43.963 --> 01:31:49.761 align:middle line:84%
Or you protected your family.

01:31:49.761 --> 01:31:52.096 align:middle line:84%
So after I put him away,

01:31:52.096 --> 01:31:53.932 align:middle line:84%
I left Samoa and I never came back.

01:31:53.932 --> 01:31:55.850 align:middle line:84%
Well, at least one good thing came out

01:31:55.850 --> 01:31:58.186 align:middle line:84%
of me jamming that thing into my hand.

01:31:58.186 --> 01:32:00.063 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, what's that?

01:32:00.063 --> 01:32:06.611 align:middle line:84%
Got to bring you home, didn't I?

01:32:06.611 --> 01:32:14.410 align:middle line:84%
Lucky me.

01:32:14.410 --> 01:32:15.828 align:middle line:84%
You went legit.

01:32:15.828 --> 01:32:18.039 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, 100% clean now.

01:32:18.039 --> 01:32:20.416 align:middle line:84%
Custom shop, international clients.

01:32:20.416 --> 01:32:22.210 align:middle line:84%
See those bikes? Going to Tokyo.

01:32:22.210 --> 01:32:23.586 align:middle line:84%
And that car? New York.

01:32:23.586 --> 01:32:25.463 align:middle line:84%
That one over there's going to London.

01:32:25.463 --> 01:32:27.966 align:middle line:84%
Turns out people like our stuff.

01:32:27.966 --> 01:32:32.095 align:middle line:90%
I needed to do something
to hold our family together.

01:32:32.095 --> 01:32:38.351 align:middle line:84%
After you abandoned us.

01:32:38.351 --> 01:32:42.772 align:middle line:84%
Hey, good news. Change of clothes. Hats.

01:32:42.772 --> 01:32:44.566 align:middle line:84%
Your mum said you might like to wear this.

01:32:44.566 --> 01:32:48.653 align:middle line:84%
Must be your favorite size. Spray on.

01:32:48.653 --> 01:32:50.029 align:middle line:84%
Why don't you throw another jacket on?

01:32:50.029 --> 01:32:51.614 align:middle line:84%
It's 110 degrees out there.

01:32:51.614 --> 01:32:56.661 align:middle line:90%
Hey, look, down to business.
We got any weapons?

01:32:56.661 --> 01:33:05.879 align:middle line:84%
Oh, we got weapons.

01:33:05.879 --> 01:33:07.422 align:middle line:84%
Mama, where's all our guns?

01:33:07.422 --> 01:33:09.966 align:middle line:84%
I get rid of 'em.

01:33:09.966 --> 01:33:12.594 align:middle line:84%
Very noble, Mrs. Hobbs.

01:33:12.594 --> 01:33:13.761 align:middle line:84%
We're in serious trouble.

01:33:13.761 --> 01:33:15.597 align:middle line:84%
That is an understatement.

01:33:15.597 --> 01:33:20.602 align:middle line:84%
These guns, they kill all my family.

01:33:20.602 --> 01:33:22.145 align:middle line:84%
So we gonna fight.

01:33:22.145 --> 01:33:26.107 align:middle line:90%
Gonna fight with this
and we gonna fight with this.

01:33:26.107 --> 01:33:29.444 align:middle line:90%
'Cause no take a real man
for pull one trigger.

01:33:29.444 --> 01:33:32.780 align:middle line:90%
All right, we're going to war
with the family heirlooms.

01:33:32.780 --> 01:33:34.574 align:middle line:84%
Got it. We're gonna need a lot more.

01:33:34.574 --> 01:33:37.076 align:middle line:84%
We're never gonna survive their firepower.

01:33:37.076 --> 01:33:39.329 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't take a man to pull a trigger,

01:33:39.329 --> 01:33:41.414 align:middle line:90%
but for Eteon,
it does take an activation chip.

01:33:41.414 --> 01:33:43.166 align:middle line:84%
You still got that glove?

01:33:43.166 --> 01:33:44.459 align:middle line:84%
You're thinking closed-system hack.

01:33:44.459 --> 01:33:46.211 align:middle line:84%
It'll level the playing field if you can.

01:33:46.211 --> 01:33:47.670 align:middle line:84%
Certainly buy us some time.

01:33:47.670 --> 01:33:48.880 align:middle line:84%
Shut their guns down.

01:33:48.880 --> 01:33:51.508 align:middle line:84%
I'm on it.

01:33:51.508 --> 01:33:55.136 align:middle line:84%
You ready?

01:33:55.136 --> 01:33:57.805 align:middle line:84%
War is what I do.

01:33:57.805 --> 01:34:00.725 align:middle line:84%
Let's go old-school.

01:34:00.725 --> 01:34:02.810 align:middle line:84%
Take a look around.

01:34:02.810 --> 01:34:04.938 align:middle line:84%
This is where we draw the line.

01:34:04.938 --> 01:34:06.022 align:middle line:84%
Who would've thought

01:34:06.022 --> 01:34:08.024 align:middle line:84%
this is where we're gonna save the world?

01:34:08.024 --> 01:34:10.235 align:middle line:84%
We need to make 'em play by our rules.

01:34:10.235 --> 01:34:12.028 align:middle line:90%
Tomorrow morning
there'll be a storm raging

01:34:12.028 --> 01:34:13.112 align:middle line:84%
on the north cliffs.

01:34:13.112 --> 01:34:14.906 align:middle line:84%
We'll build a no-man's-land there.

01:34:14.906 --> 01:34:19.160 align:middle line:90%
And if all else fails,
that'll be our last stand.

01:34:19.160 --> 01:34:22.830 align:middle line:84%
How many more of these we gotta do?

01:34:22.830 --> 01:34:24.999 align:middle line:84%
Just keep digging, brother.

01:34:24.999 --> 01:34:27.126 align:middle line:90%
When we were
in Kandahar running raids,

01:34:27.126 --> 01:34:29.796 align:middle line:90%
Brixton would always strike
just before dawn.

01:34:29.796 --> 01:34:31.422 align:middle line:84%
It's when the enemy's most tired,

01:34:31.422 --> 01:34:34.092 align:middle line:84%
still under the cover of night.

01:34:34.092 --> 01:34:35.718 align:middle line:84%
When the battle shifts into high gear,

01:34:35.718 --> 01:34:37.470 align:middle line:84%
you got the sun at your back.

01:34:37.470 --> 01:34:38.972 align:middle line:84%
We let 'em all in.

01:34:38.972 --> 01:34:40.807 align:middle line:84%
And we make sure they never leave.

01:34:40.807 --> 01:34:46.062 align:middle line:90%
Kill box. I like it.
Not like we got a ton of resources.

01:34:46.062 --> 01:36:28.706 align:middle line:84%
But the island will provide, brother.

01:36:28.706 --> 01:36:30.208 align:middle line:84%
Give me the good news, Hat.

01:36:30.208 --> 01:36:31.626 align:middle line:84%
I'm in. The only thing is,

01:36:31.626 --> 01:36:33.670 align:middle line:90%
I could only block the signal
repeaters on the satellite

01:36:33.670 --> 01:36:35.129 align:middle line:84%
for six minutes.

01:36:35.129 --> 01:36:37.799 align:middle line:84%
Six minutes might be all the time we need.

01:36:37.799 --> 01:36:39.217 align:middle line:84%
Better than a sharp stick in the eye.

01:36:39.217 --> 01:36:40.927 align:middle line:84%
Which is basically all we've got

01:36:40.927 --> 01:36:42.136 align:middle line:84%
to fight them with anyway.

01:36:42.136 --> 01:37:01.865 align:middle line:84%
Done more with less, haven't we?

01:37:01.865 --> 01:37:04.951 align:middle line:84%
Hi.

01:37:04.951 --> 01:37:12.125 align:middle line:90%
- Drink?
- Sure. Thank you.

01:37:12.125 --> 01:37:13.501 align:middle line:84%
Just taking it all in,

01:37:13.501 --> 01:37:22.468 align:middle line:84%
in case it's the last sunset we see.

01:37:22.468 --> 01:37:30.435 align:middle line:90%
I shouldn't have believed
that Deckard went dark.

01:37:30.435 --> 01:37:39.694 align:middle line:84%
Wasted so much time. I'm...

01:37:39.694 --> 01:37:44.115 align:middle line:84%
I've spent my whole life running away.

01:37:44.115 --> 01:37:45.783 align:middle line:84%
Me too.

01:37:45.783 --> 01:37:48.036 align:middle line:84%
Yeah?

01:37:48.036 --> 01:37:51.289 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

01:37:51.289 --> 01:37:52.957 align:middle line:84%
I haven't been back here in 25 years.

01:37:52.957 --> 01:37:57.462 align:middle line:90%
I mean, my own daughter
doesn't even know her family.

01:37:57.462 --> 01:38:06.054 align:middle line:84%
Well... you can change that.

01:38:06.054 --> 01:38:08.223 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

01:38:08.223 --> 01:38:10.850 align:middle line:84%
So can you.

01:38:10.850 --> 01:38:12.477 align:middle line:84%
I got an idea. Why don't you and I

01:38:12.477 --> 01:38:14.771 align:middle line:84%
make a promise right here, right now?

01:38:14.771 --> 01:38:17.273 align:middle line:84%
That when we see tomorrow's sunset,

01:38:17.273 --> 01:38:30.203 align:middle line:84%
we begin to fix the mistakes we've made.

01:38:30.203 --> 01:38:36.709 align:middle line:90%
That's just sealed it so you
can't back out. That's all.

01:38:36.709 --> 01:38:38.419 align:middle line:84%
I don't think there's any chance in hell

01:38:38.419 --> 01:38:40.839 align:middle line:84%
I would back out.

01:38:40.839 --> 01:38:42.632 align:middle line:84%
You wanna seal it again or...

01:38:42.632 --> 01:38:44.717 align:middle line:90%
- Definitely not.
- Okay.

01:38:44.717 --> 01:38:49.305 align:middle line:84%
Maybe tomorrow, if I survive.

01:38:49.305 --> 01:38:50.890 align:middle line:90%
- Jonah.
- Look, don't rush me.

01:38:50.890 --> 01:38:53.518 align:middle line:90%
It's almost dawn.
He'll be here soon.

01:38:53.518 --> 01:38:55.603 align:middle line:84%
Make it happen now! Now!

01:38:55.603 --> 01:38:57.897 align:middle line:90%
Hey, hey, don't rush me.
That's how mistakes are made.

01:38:57.897 --> 01:38:59.941 align:middle line:84%
And how long does this process take?

01:38:59.941 --> 01:39:02.235 align:middle line:84%
It's 30 minutes and 33 till I go viral.

01:39:02.235 --> 01:39:04.737 align:middle line:90%
Look, Deck, I think we need to
seriously consider option one.

01:39:04.737 --> 01:39:06.656 align:middle line:84%
Don't strike a match just yet, Hats.

01:39:06.656 --> 01:39:08.491 align:middle line:84%
We are seriously gonna miss this window.

01:39:08.491 --> 01:39:10.785 align:middle line:90%
- Let's do this. Come on!
- Jonah, now!

01:39:10.785 --> 01:39:14.831 align:middle line:84%
Fine, fine, okay. Here goes nothing.

01:39:14.831 --> 01:39:17.792 align:middle line:84%
Brace yourself, Hats.

01:39:17.792 --> 01:39:19.127 align:middle line:84%
It ain't gonna be pleasant.

01:39:19.127 --> 01:39:35.768 align:middle line:84%
No, it's gonna be fine.

01:39:35.768 --> 01:39:37.520 align:middle line:84%
It's working. It's working.

01:39:37.520 --> 01:39:39.480 align:middle line:84%
Yeah.

01:39:39.480 --> 01:39:44.527 align:middle line:84%
Yeah!

01:39:44.527 --> 01:39:45.945 align:middle line:84%
Hey.

01:39:45.945 --> 01:39:47.614 align:middle line:84%
They triggered the alarm!

01:39:47.614 --> 01:39:49.365 align:middle line:84%
That's him.

01:39:49.365 --> 01:39:55.914 align:middle line:90%
- As we planned?
- As we planned.

01:39:55.914 --> 01:40:01.044 align:middle line:84%
It's time.

01:40:01.044 --> 01:40:06.966 align:middle line:84%
Jonah.

01:40:06.966 --> 01:40:09.969 align:middle line:84%
Just wanna say that, uh...

01:40:09.969 --> 01:40:13.139 align:middle line:84%
if this thing goes sideways and...

01:40:13.139 --> 01:40:17.810 align:middle line:84%
and this is it...

01:40:17.810 --> 01:40:21.231 align:middle line:84%
I'm sorry.

01:40:21.231 --> 01:40:26.653 align:middle line:90%
I may have had my reasons,
but the fact is...

01:40:26.653 --> 01:40:33.952 align:middle line:84%
I left you and I left our 'aiga.

01:40:33.952 --> 01:40:36.496 align:middle line:84%
I should've come home.

01:40:36.496 --> 01:40:38.456 align:middle line:84%
If we make it through this,

01:40:38.456 --> 01:40:44.504 align:middle line:90%
you have my word I'll never
let that happen again.

01:40:44.504 --> 01:40:54.138 align:middle line:84%
I love you, uso.

01:40:54.138 --> 01:41:02.856 align:middle line:84%
I love you too, uso.

01:41:02.856 --> 01:41:08.695 align:middle line:84%
Okay, you're mobile.

01:41:08.695 --> 01:41:10.697 align:middle line:90%
Do you think I need to be
so close to the front line?

01:41:10.697 --> 01:41:12.824 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, we keep you close.
Keep an eye on you

01:41:12.824 --> 01:41:14.742 align:middle line:84%
in case we need to make a quick getaway.

01:41:14.742 --> 01:41:17.871 align:middle line:84%
Hey, this is what we do, right?

01:41:17.871 --> 01:41:21.583 align:middle line:84%
It is what we do.

01:41:21.583 --> 01:41:26.713 align:middle line:84%
Deck...

01:41:26.713 --> 01:41:31.092 align:middle line:84%
I overheard what Brixton said.

01:41:31.092 --> 01:41:35.597 align:middle line:84%
That you stayed away to protect us.

01:41:35.597 --> 01:41:40.560 align:middle line:90%
I never should've believed
all that stuff, I know it now.

01:41:40.560 --> 01:41:42.562 align:middle line:84%
I don't know why I did. I'm so sorry.

01:41:42.562 --> 01:41:44.606 align:middle line:84%
Don't be.

01:41:44.606 --> 01:41:48.026 align:middle line:84%
Don't be. Hey, look, I've done things,

01:41:48.026 --> 01:41:51.070 align:middle line:84%
done things I'm not proud of.

01:41:51.070 --> 01:41:54.741 align:middle line:84%
Things I... have to make amends for.

01:41:54.741 --> 01:41:58.536 align:middle line:90%
All thanks to what
that bastard put me through.

01:41:58.536 --> 01:42:01.456 align:middle line:90%
But right now,
the most important thing to me

01:42:01.456 --> 01:42:34.822 align:middle line:84%
is getting my little sister home safely.

01:42:34.822 --> 01:42:53.299 align:middle line:84%
Eteon, hold!

01:42:53.299 --> 01:42:58.471 align:middle line:84%
Brothers of Samoa!

01:42:58.471 --> 01:43:07.856 align:middle line:84%
We call upon our Gods and ancestors

01:43:07.856 --> 01:43:14.988 align:middle line:90%
to ask for strength,
for now is the time for war!

01:43:14.988 --> 01:43:18.157 align:middle line:84%
Rise!

01:43:18.157 --> 01:43:24.455 align:middle line:90%
- Do it.
- Light 'em up.

01:43:24.455 --> 01:43:28.960 align:middle line:84%
What's going on?

01:43:28.960 --> 01:43:30.962 align:middle line:84%
How long before the guns get back online?

01:43:30.962 --> 01:43:33.339 align:middle line:84%
I've no idea.

01:43:33.339 --> 01:43:34.424 align:middle line:84%
Look into my eyes!

01:43:34.424 --> 01:43:44.225 align:middle line:90%
They will be the last thing
you see before you die!

01:43:44.225 --> 01:44:02.452 align:middle line:84%
To war!

01:44:02.452 --> 01:44:09.250 align:middle line:84%
Shaw.

01:44:09.250 --> 01:44:12.128 align:middle line:84%
Air command.

01:44:12.128 --> 01:45:24.367 align:middle line:84%
Bring me the chopper.

01:45:24.367 --> 01:45:44.387 align:middle line:84%
Deck!

01:45:44.387 --> 01:45:46.055 align:middle line:84%
Do it quick, Hats.

01:45:46.055 --> 01:45:47.849 align:middle line:84%
It's in, it's in, it's in. Is it working?

01:45:47.849 --> 01:45:50.852 align:middle line:84%
Machine's on.

01:45:50.852 --> 01:45:52.061 align:middle line:90%
- We're good.
- We're good.

01:45:52.061 --> 01:47:04.217 align:middle line:84%
Let's go.

01:47:04.217 --> 01:47:29.033 align:middle line:84%
Hobbs!

01:47:29.033 --> 01:47:33.955 align:middle line:84%
Go, go!

01:47:33.955 --> 01:47:35.373 align:middle line:84%
Let's go fishing, Shaw.

01:47:35.373 --> 01:47:43.006 align:middle line:84%
You catch him, I'll gut him.

01:47:43.006 --> 01:48:06.237 align:middle line:84%
Hold on!

01:48:06.237 --> 01:48:21.503 align:middle line:90%
- Welcome to my island, you...
- Take it up!

01:48:21.503 --> 01:48:23.713 align:middle line:84%
You get us close and I'll get her.

01:48:23.713 --> 01:48:35.808 align:middle line:84%
I'll keep his nose down. You reel him in.

01:48:35.808 --> 01:48:47.195 align:middle line:84%
Take it up! Take it up!

01:48:47.195 --> 01:49:05.255 align:middle line:84%
Have a day off.

01:49:05.255 --> 01:49:06.840 align:middle line:84%
What are you doing?

01:49:06.840 --> 01:49:13.513 align:middle line:84%
We're going for a ride.

01:49:13.513 --> 01:49:14.973 align:middle line:84%
Shit.

01:49:14.973 --> 01:49:19.519 align:middle line:84%
We're coming, usos!

01:49:19.519 --> 01:49:23.481 align:middle line:84%
Ha-ha!

01:49:23.481 --> 01:49:24.566 align:middle line:84%
Let's go, Jonah.

01:49:24.566 --> 01:49:27.694 align:middle line:84%
Come on, brother.

01:49:27.694 --> 01:49:48.173 align:middle line:84%
The axle, the axle!

01:49:48.173 --> 01:50:03.521 align:middle line:84%
Timo, you got this!

01:50:03.521 --> 01:50:05.857 align:middle line:84%
We're gonna need more weight.

01:50:05.857 --> 01:50:16.868 align:middle line:84%
Whoo-hoo-hoo! Yeah!

01:50:16.868 --> 01:50:22.290 align:middle line:84%
Bring it in nice and easy, clean.

01:50:22.290 --> 01:50:26.544 align:middle line:84%
Hell yeah, usos!

01:50:26.544 --> 01:50:39.432 align:middle line:90%
- It's too much weight!
- All right, drop 'em.

01:50:39.432 --> 01:50:46.272 align:middle line:84%
Stay there!

01:50:46.272 --> 01:51:15.009 align:middle line:84%
Hit 'em with the moonshine! Now!

01:51:15.009 --> 01:51:21.975 align:middle line:84%
Hang me off a cliff, huh? My turn.

01:51:21.975 --> 01:51:23.601 align:middle line:84%
Sir, the weapons are back online.

01:51:23.601 --> 01:51:26.229 align:middle line:84%
Let's go, let's go!

01:51:26.229 --> 01:51:28.857 align:middle line:84%
Goodbye.

01:51:28.857 --> 01:51:40.368 align:middle line:84%
Incoming!

01:51:40.368 --> 01:51:42.203 align:middle line:84%
We got a little trouble back here, Shaw.

01:51:42.203 --> 01:51:56.759 align:middle line:84%
We'll lose 'em in no-man's-land.

01:51:56.759 --> 01:52:15.278 align:middle line:84%
Let's get this up!

01:52:15.278 --> 01:52:31.419 align:middle line:84%
All right, now hit that stake.

01:52:31.419 --> 01:52:34.422 align:middle line:84%
We're losing the rotor!

01:52:34.422 --> 01:52:40.887 align:middle line:84%
Shit.

01:52:40.887 --> 01:52:44.182 align:middle line:84%
What the...

01:52:44.182 --> 01:52:53.191 align:middle line:84%
I got you, Hobbs.

01:52:53.191 --> 01:53:00.448 align:middle line:84%
Hey!

01:53:00.448 --> 01:53:06.621 align:middle line:90%
- The rotor!
- Losing power.

01:53:06.621 --> 01:54:00.800 align:middle line:90%
- Guys!
- Hattie! Jump!

01:54:00.800 --> 01:54:03.511 align:middle line:84%
Hey, get up. Get up!

01:54:03.511 --> 01:54:05.388 align:middle line:84%
Hey! Get up!

01:54:05.388 --> 01:54:07.724 align:middle line:84%
You don't die until I tell you to die.

01:54:07.724 --> 01:54:09.309 align:middle line:84%
You see the extraction timer?

01:54:09.309 --> 01:54:11.186 align:middle line:84%
When it hits zero,

01:54:11.186 --> 01:54:23.948 align:middle line:90%
empty this clip into her heart,
do you understand?

01:54:23.948 --> 01:54:28.745 align:middle line:84%
Hattie!

01:54:28.745 --> 01:54:31.039 align:middle line:84%
This doesn't end your way, boys.

01:54:31.039 --> 01:54:33.124 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, you keep telling yourself that.

01:54:33.124 --> 01:54:36.294 align:middle line:84%
Ah, the numbers don't add up for you.

01:54:36.294 --> 01:54:38.171 align:middle line:84%
The evolution of man is coming,

01:54:38.171 --> 01:54:42.592 align:middle line:84%
whether you like it or not.

01:54:42.592 --> 01:54:44.719 align:middle line:84%
You know, I almost feel bad for you.

01:54:44.719 --> 01:54:47.138 align:middle line:90%
'Cause it's not just metal
they filled your head with.

01:54:47.138 --> 01:54:51.017 align:middle line:84%
It's bullshit.

01:54:51.017 --> 01:54:54.938 align:middle line:90%
I was beginning to like you two,
you know that?

01:54:54.938 --> 01:55:31.891 align:middle line:84%
Oh, well.

01:55:31.891 --> 01:55:35.228 align:middle line:84%
What's the problem, boys? Does it hurt?

01:55:35.228 --> 01:56:09.596 align:middle line:84%
Must be hard being so... human.

01:56:09.596 --> 01:56:10.889 align:middle line:90%
- Did you see that?
- Yeah.

01:56:10.889 --> 01:56:12.640 align:middle line:84%
We work together, we can hurt him.

01:56:12.640 --> 01:56:14.184 align:middle line:84%
You're right.

01:56:14.184 --> 01:56:15.268 align:middle line:84%
Time to work as a team.

01:56:15.268 --> 01:56:16.853 align:middle line:84%
There's two of us and one of him.

01:56:16.853 --> 01:56:18.855 align:middle line:84%
I'll take a punch and let you land one.

01:56:18.855 --> 01:56:21.274 align:middle line:84%
I'll do the same.

01:56:21.274 --> 01:56:22.483 align:middle line:84%
I got your back, brother.

01:56:22.483 --> 01:56:24.569 align:middle line:84%
And I got yours.

01:56:24.569 --> 01:58:18.766 align:middle line:84%
Let's go unplug this sumbitch.

01:58:18.766 --> 01:58:36.075 align:middle line:84%
Here comes the kryptonite.

01:58:36.075 --> 01:58:37.702 align:middle line:84%
I got it.

01:58:37.702 --> 01:58:39.287 align:middle line:84%
You did it, Hat.

01:58:39.287 --> 01:58:42.165 align:middle line:84%
Never had a doubt.

01:58:42.165 --> 01:58:49.964 align:middle line:84%
Let's get it into safe hands.

01:58:49.964 --> 01:58:53.301 align:middle line:84%
You set me up as a traitor.

01:58:53.301 --> 01:58:56.721 align:middle line:84%
Turned my own sister against me.

01:58:56.721 --> 01:59:00.725 align:middle line:84%
Forced me to kill my own brother. You.

01:59:00.725 --> 01:59:04.771 align:middle line:84%
And here we are again. Come on!

01:59:04.771 --> 01:59:10.193 align:middle line:84%
Shaw, compared to the cause...

01:59:10.193 --> 01:59:12.654 align:middle line:84%
one life doesn't mean anything.

01:59:12.654 --> 01:59:17.742 align:middle line:90%
I don't know
what happened to you, Brixton.

01:59:17.742 --> 01:59:21.788 align:middle line:84%
But you made me kill you once.

01:59:21.788 --> 01:59:28.545 align:middle line:84%
I ain't doing it again.

01:59:28.545 --> 01:59:32.257 align:middle line:84%
Brother, you may believe in machines...

01:59:32.257 --> 01:59:41.975 align:middle line:84%
but we believe in people.

01:59:41.975 --> 01:59:48.356 align:middle line:90%
You may have all
the technology in the world.

01:59:48.356 --> 01:59:51.442 align:middle line:84%
We have heart.

01:59:51.442 --> 01:59:56.447 align:middle line:84%
No machine will ever beat that.

01:59:56.447 --> 02:00:09.502 align:middle line:90%
You boys, you're gonna get
one Samoan ass-whupping.

02:00:09.502 --> 02:00:20.263 align:middle line:84%
Shut Brixton down.

02:00:20.263 --> 02:00:25.768 align:middle line:84%
So that's how it is?

02:00:25.768 --> 02:00:45.872 align:middle line:84%
It's a hell of business, boys.

02:00:45.872 --> 02:00:47.290 align:middle line:84%
Brixton never really

02:00:47.290 --> 02:00:50.043 align:middle line:84%
lived up to our expectations.

02:00:50.043 --> 02:00:55.131 align:middle line:90%
But you three,
you outperformed your analytics.

02:00:55.131 --> 02:00:59.052 align:middle line:84%
You don't remember me, do you, Hobbs?

02:00:59.052 --> 02:01:01.095 align:middle line:84%
You will.

02:01:01.095 --> 02:01:05.099 align:middle line:84%
It's gonna be a hell of reunion.

02:01:05.099 --> 02:01:08.228 align:middle line:84%
You're on our radar now.

02:01:08.228 --> 02:01:18.655 align:middle line:84%
And you're on ours.

02:01:18.655 --> 02:01:20.114 align:middle line:84%
Hey, thanks for being my sidekick

02:01:20.114 --> 02:01:21.366 align:middle line:84%
through this whole thing, brother.

02:01:21.366 --> 02:01:22.659 align:middle line:84%
You were great.

02:01:22.659 --> 02:01:23.743 align:middle line:84%
Hey, how 'bout I side-kick

02:01:23.743 --> 02:01:24.911 align:middle line:84%
that stupid look off your face?

02:01:24.911 --> 02:01:26.538 align:middle line:84%
Yeah? How 'bout you show me right now?

02:01:26.538 --> 02:01:28.456 align:middle line:84%
Okay, guys.

02:01:28.456 --> 02:01:32.627 align:middle line:84%
Let's go home.

02:01:32.627 --> 02:01:35.630 align:middle line:90%
- Yeah.
- All right.

02:01:35.630 --> 02:01:37.048 align:middle line:84%
Look, Batman had Robin.

02:01:37.048 --> 02:01:38.967 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Evil had Mini-Me. You're my Mini-Me.

02:01:38.967 --> 02:01:41.636 align:middle line:90%
Han Solo had Chewbacca.
Kermit had Miss Piggy.

02:01:41.636 --> 02:01:43.054 align:middle line:84%
That's a low blow. Don't say that.

02:01:43.054 --> 02:01:44.138 align:middle line:84%
Don't argue with me on my island.

02:01:44.138 --> 02:02:45.408 align:middle line:84%
You're my sidekick.

02:02:45.408 --> 02:02:49.787 align:middle line:84%
I'm so happy you're back.

02:02:49.787 --> 02:02:53.208 align:middle line:84%
Brought you that cake you wanted.

02:02:53.208 --> 02:02:57.712 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't eat it.

02:02:57.712 --> 02:03:06.429 align:middle line:84%
Let's get out of here.

02:03:06.429 --> 02:03:10.725 align:middle line:84%
How long have you been working here?

02:03:10.725 --> 02:03:22.695 align:middle line:84%
Sam, this is your grandma.

02:03:22.695 --> 02:03:27.742 align:middle line:84%
I love you.

02:03:27.742 --> 02:03:30.119 align:middle line:84%
Good to have you home, uso.

02:03:30.119 --> 02:04:00.608 align:middle line:84%
It's good to be home, uso.

02:04:00.608 --> 02:04:02.443 align:middle line:90%
Hobbs.
I hope you're sitting down, buddy,

02:04:02.443 --> 02:04:03.736 align:middle line:84%
because we got big problems.

02:04:03.736 --> 02:04:06.322 align:middle line:90%
God. I feel immediately better
just talking to you.

02:04:06.322 --> 02:04:07.574 align:middle line:84%
Is that weird?

02:04:07.574 --> 02:04:10.535 align:middle line:90%
Anyway, look.
The Snowflake virus, totally fine.

02:04:10.535 --> 02:04:12.537 align:middle line:84%
On lockdown. In a secure asset vault.

02:04:12.537 --> 02:04:17.709 align:middle line:90%
But what we're dealing with right now...
is another virus.

02:04:17.709 --> 02:04:20.420 align:middle line:90%
The last one, well,
that melted your insides,

02:04:20.420 --> 02:04:21.921 align:middle line:84%
but this one...

02:04:21.921 --> 02:04:24.632 align:middle line:84%
melts your outsides. Literally.

02:04:24.632 --> 02:04:26.050 align:middle line:84%
Your skin drips off.

02:04:26.050 --> 02:04:28.720 align:middle line:90%
It's like removing
a silk kimono in a hurricane.

02:04:28.720 --> 02:04:29.804 align:middle line:84%
It's so gross.

02:04:29.804 --> 02:04:33.224 align:middle line:90%
The point is we need to
get on this, like, now.

02:04:33.224 --> 02:04:35.143 align:middle line:84%
I need both of you.

02:04:35.143 --> 02:04:36.227 align:middle line:84%
What do you say, Becky?

02:04:36.227 --> 02:04:38.479 align:middle line:90%
- Hey, Locke. This is Sam.
- Sam?

02:04:38.479 --> 02:04:39.606 align:middle line:84%
You must wanna talk to my dad.

02:04:39.606 --> 02:04:42.025 align:middle line:84%
Oh, my God. Sam.

02:04:42.025 --> 02:04:47.113 align:middle line:84%
Wow! You sound exactly like your dad.

02:04:47.113 --> 02:04:49.365 align:middle line:84%
